{"tid":753922,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企老母日日寵住個港女家姐，想死","createTime":"2018-07-24T04:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T04:59:31.000Z","uid":172451,"like":61,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"daa95a84d9dd009e6cba9b71e5308739790a7d09","tid":753922,"uid":172451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T04:12:06.000Z","msg":"點我做野仲要冇禮貌又串柒柒，肥過欣宜仲可以係出面收兵，成日FF自己同韓星拍拖，其實王晶咁既樣都益撚左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做人無品又貪小便宜，試過我有朋友上黎屋企坐，佢竟然要我朋友落街幫佢買奶茶，仲唔俾返錢我朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我知道左之後面都紅埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但最撚慘既係我老母唔知點解錫到佢濃，仲話第時身家分大份啲既俾佢，啲人話屋企會錫細仔多啲我完全唔撚覺囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日我仲要行行下街冇撚左data，原來老母連family plan啲data都分大份既俾佢，仆佢個街全屋四個人成40gb data，兩老各10gb，佢就15gb，我分得果5gb！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果5gb俾乞衣架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上下連登碌下facebook都冇撚左啦屌，我同老母講，佢話家姐要做野要用多d，仲話我男人老狗玩咁多手機做咩，出下打d波啦咪留係屋企咁多啦，你老味冇data我連飛機都打唔到呀屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a190e2edca8eea34fc8fc4ef3fe59073c8dfb2","tid":753922,"uid":138138,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T04:13:11.000Z","msg":"肥過欣宜？ <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/121302_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F121302_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=05f64696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我要圖阿"},{"pid":"a8d13333966caac66708f343400fca1f41bb9aef","tid":753922,"uid":134474,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T04:13:55.000Z","msg":"你幾歲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己再開張卡啦，得嗰5gb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7292b6f4ba26dcb72c8964efc9528355ec1a97bd","tid":753922,"uid":193957,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T04:15:56.000Z","msg":"一個小六一個小四呀？"},{"pid":"e727407f298fd1894ba22d87f34a885c6a92647f","tid":753922,"uid":43530,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T04:17:14.000Z","msg":"5G 我讀中學個陣日日返學,,冇得用電話都唔夠用啦<br />\n自己開張卡,無限上網先300銀左右<br />\n<br />\nBTW 家姐相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c3e19b21992738782b588ced135f8e879f2a0f","tid":753922,"uid":188637,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T04:30:39.000Z","msg":"一個月用唔到 3G... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6139c2e9206137e02bb55c82ff33b49847a719f","tid":753922,"uid":171760,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T07:42:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8651a66de95666bc1295b620151ab13835abaa25","tid":753922,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T07:44:58.000Z","msg":"肥過欣宜仲可以係出面收兵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc3271603005191f177b6cd6b7fff2dbecd125c","tid":753922,"uid":33004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c6139c2e9206137e02bb55c82ff33b49847a719f","tid":753922,"uid":171